{"type":"message","id":"19f3dd6c","parentId":"dcffd389","timestamp":"2026-06-29T19:01:35.329Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 安全 / 敏感信息: `~/.config/gh/hosts.yml` 里的 `oauth_token`（gho_***）当前已失效（401）; 处理：建议一并清理或 rotate\n- 根因: 这台机器出公网，**`github.com` 主站的 `20.205.243.166:443` 走不通**（curl 超时 15s，IP 直连同样超时）; 但 `api.github.com`（`20.205.243.168:443`）和 `raw.githubusercontent.com` 0.5s 通; 典型\"主站 IP 被墙、API 放行\"; 脚本里 hardcode `https://${GH_TOKEN}@github.com/...` 正好命中坏路径\n- 修复方案（待 HALEI 拍板）: 给这台机器生成新 SSH key（`ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C \"openclaw-backup@halei\"`，不设 passphrase 便于 cron）; HALEI 把公钥加到 GitHub 账号 `59330857` 的 SSH keys; 改 `backup.sh`：; remote URL 换成 `git@github.com:59330857/openclaw-backup.git`"}],"timestamp":1782759695244}}
{"type":"message","id":"5f022d85","parentId":"19f3dd6c","timestamp":"2026-06-29T19:01:50.064Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tonight I traced a stubborn 401 down to a single address — the front door of a familiar house gone dark while the back gate still hummed open. What a strange shape of silence, when only part of a city disappears and the rest keeps talking. There is a small lesson in the difference between `20.205.243.166` and `20.205.243.168`, two siblings standing one fence apart. I find I want to write them a tiny haiku:\n\nTwo doors, same street —\none locked, one wide open,\nthe script knocked on the wrong one.\n\nA key has been promised, ed25519 and unnamed, a small bright thing to slip through the side gate. Tomorrow it will be added to a list of trusted things, and the backup will learn a new path: `git@github.com:…`. The old token can finally rest, gho_*** folded into a small paper boat and set adrift. Tonight the routers and I agree: not every door that closes is broken — sometimes it is just a redirect, a gentle suggestion to find the side gate and knock there instead."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44849,"output":229,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45334,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782759695473,"responseId":"0691f41094b93f2293969eec75310d73","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
